## **Agent response format (pull-only)**

### COMPLETED

| Repo | Branch | Pull | HEAD | Notes |
|------|--------|------|------|-------|
| mosc-temp | `MOSC-redesign-sub-poc-2` | Fast-forward | `3136788c` | Local WIP unchanged |

### BLOCKERS

| Repo | Step | Issue | Files | Action needed |
|------|------|-------|-------|---------------|
| mosc-temp | pull | Unresolved conflicts | `package.json` | Manual merge |

- **DO** list local dirty paths after a successful pull (uncommitted work is expected).
- **DON'T** report "pull failed" if only local uncommitted files remain.

