## **Anti-patterns**

```powershell
# ❌ DON'T: Commit or push during a pull-only request
# ❌ DON'T: git reset --hard without user approval (destroys local WIP)
# ❌ DON'T: Skip fetch before pull
# ❌ DON'T: git config http.sslVerify false globally
# ❌ DON'T: Leave conflict markers and report success
# ❌ DON'T: stash pop blindly on generated test reports without checking if remote should win
```

